<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>RagChew — Amateur Radio Net Tracker</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A mobile app for following amateur radio nets on iOS and Android. See active nets, check-in lists, net chat, and more.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --blue:       #2563EB;
      --blue-light: #3B82F6;
      --blue-dim:   rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
      --bg:         #0D1117;
      --bg-card:    #161B22;
      --bg-card2:   #1C2330;
      --border:     rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --text:       #F0F6FC;
      --muted:      #8B949E;
      --radius:     16px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    html, body { overflow-x: hidden; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 5%;
      height: 64px;
      background: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .nav-logo img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .top-banner {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 14px auto 0;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
      border-radius: 18px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(28, 35, 48, 0.92), rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.96)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
      overflow: hidden;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .top-banner::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 0 auto 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.28), transparent);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .top-banner-copy {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      color: #eef4ff;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .top-banner-copy strong {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .top-banner-link {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.16);
      border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.28);
      color: #eff6ff;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .top-banner-link:hover {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.24);
      border-color: rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.56);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 9px 18px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      color: var(--muted);
      background: transparent;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--text); background: var(--border); }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--blue-light); }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 96px 5% 80px;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto 44px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .store-buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .store-badges {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .store-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
    }

    .store-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      opacity: 0.96;
    }

    .store-btn img {
      display: block;
      height: 56px;
      width: auto;
    }

    .store-btn-disabled {
      pointer-events: none;
      cursor: default;
      opacity: 0.42;
      filter: grayscale(1) saturate(0.2);
    }

    .store-btn-google img {
      height: 84px;
    }

    .android-section {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .android-beta-notice {
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      max-width: 420px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.26);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.16), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.06)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    }

    .android-beta-copy {
      max-width: 310px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: #dce9ff;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .android-beta-copy strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .android-beta-notice button {
      border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.16);
      color: #eff6ff;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .android-beta-notice button:hover {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.24);
      border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.7);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    dialog {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 50% auto auto 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 32px;
      max-width: 420px;
      width: calc(100vw - 48px);
    }

    dialog::backdrop {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }

    dialog h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    dialog p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    dialog .dialog-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    dialog .btn-close {
      background: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: inherit;
      padding: 9px 18px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    dialog .btn-close:hover { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── Screenshots ── */
    .screenshots-section {
      padding: 20px 0 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .screenshots-track {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 20px 5% 28px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      -ms-overflow-style: none;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      scroll-padding-inline: 5%;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }
    .screenshots-track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .screenshot-item {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      scroll-snap-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .screenshot-item img {
      height: 520px;
      max-width: min(78vw, 320px);
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 32px;
      display: block;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.08),
        0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    /* ── Features ── */
    .features-section {
      padding: 80px 5%;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .section-header p {
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      background: var(--blue-dim);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Web version strip ── */
    .web-strip {
      margin: 0 5% 80px;
      padding: 36px 40px;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .web-strip-text h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .web-strip-text p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 40px 5%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .footer-logo img {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 80px;
        padding-bottom: 64px;
      }

      .hero-sub {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .screenshots-section {
        padding-bottom: 64px;
      }

      .screenshots-track {
        justify-content: flex-start;
        gap: 16px;
        padding-inline: 24px;
        scroll-padding-inline: 24px;
      }

      .screenshot-item img {
        height: min(72vh, 480px);
        max-width: min(76vw, 300px);
        border-radius: 28px;
      }

      .features-section {
        padding-top: 64px;
        padding-bottom: 64px;
      }

      .section-header {
        margin-bottom: 36px;
      }

      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav {
        height: auto;
        min-height: 64px;
        padding-top: 12px;
        padding-bottom: 12px;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .nav-logo {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .nav-links {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .nav-links .btn-ghost {
        display: inline-flex;
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 56px 5% 48px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 10vw, 2.8rem);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .hero-sub {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .store-buttons {
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .store-btn {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 240px;
      }

      .screenshots-section {
        padding-top: 8px;
        padding-bottom: 48px;
      }

      .screenshots-track {
        padding-inline: 16px;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        scroll-padding-inline: 16px;
      }

      .screenshot-item img {
        height: auto;
        width: min(82vw, 300px);
        max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .features-section {
        padding: 56px 5%;
      }

      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .feature-card {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .feature-card p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .web-strip {
        margin-bottom: 56px;
        padding: 24px 20px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .web-strip .btn {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      footer {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding-top: 32px;
      }

      .footer-links {
        gap: 14px 18px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 400px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 44px;
      }

      .top-banner {
        width: calc(100% - 20px);
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 16px 14px;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .top-banner-copy {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .top-banner-copy strong {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
      }

      .top-banner-copy span {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }

      .store-buttons {
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .store-btn {
        min-width: 0;
      }

      .screenshot-item img {
        width: 86vw;
      }

      .feature-card {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
      <img src="/images/app-icon.png" alt="RagChew icon">
      RagChew
    </a>
  </nav>

  <div class="top-banner">
    <p class="top-banner-copy">
      <strong>Use the web version for free at ragchew.site</strong>
    </p>
    <a href="https://ragchew.site" class="top-banner-link">Open ragchew.site &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>RagChew</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A mobile app for following amateur radio nets. See who's on the air, browse check-in lists, read net chat, and track your favorite stations — on iOS and Android.</p>
    <div class="store-buttons">
      <div class="store-badges">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ragchew/id6759530894?ct=app_landing" class="store-btn store-btn-apple" aria-label="Download on the App Store">
          <img src="/images/store-badges/download-on-the-app-store.svg" alt="Download on the App Store">
        </a>
        <div class="android-section">
          <!-- TODO: replace # with real Google Play URL -->
        <a href="#" class="store-btn store-btn-google store-btn-disabled" aria-label="Get it on Google Play" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1">
          <img src="/images/store-badges/google-play-badge.png" alt="Get it on Google Play">
        </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="android-beta-notice">
        <span class="android-beta-copy">
          <strong>Android early access</strong>
          Not currently on the Play Store &mdash; we need Android beta testers.
        </span>
        <button onclick="document.getElementById('beta-dialog').showModal()">Become an Android Beta Tester</button>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Screenshots -->
  <section class="screenshots-section">
    <div class="screenshots-track">
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/screenshots/screenshot-5.png" alt="RagChew profile and navigation">
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/screenshots/screenshot-1.png" alt="Net details with live status and map">
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/screenshots/screenshot-3.png" alt="Check-in list for a net">
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/screenshots/screenshot-2.png" alt="Live net chat">
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/screenshots/screenshot-4.png" alt="Club and group details">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>What's in the app</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📡</div>
        <h3>Active Nets</h3>
        <p>A live list of nets currently on the air, with frequency, mode, band, and start time. Updates automatically in the background.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>Check-in List</h3>
        <p>The full check-in log for any net, searchable by callsign, name, or remarks. Stations with grid squares appear on a map.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
        <h3>Net Chat</h3>
        <p>Read and send instant messages on any net you're monitoring. Requires a QRZ account to participate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
        <h3>Favorites &amp; Notifications</h3>
        <p>Get push notifications when a favorited net starts or a favorited station checks into any net.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🏛️</div>
        <h3>Clubs &amp; Groups</h3>
        <p>A directory of amateur radio clubs, each listing the nets associated with that club.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Closed Nets</h3>
        <p>Browse nets that have recently closed. Filter by date range or search by name.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Web version strip -->
  <div class="web-strip">
    <div class="web-strip-text">
      <h3>Also available on the web</h3>
      <p>ragchew.site has the same data in a browser.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="https://ragchew.site" class="btn btn-ghost" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);">
      ragchew.site &rarr;
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-logo">
      <img src="/images/app-icon.png" alt="RagChew icon">
      RagChew
    </div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="https://ragchew.site/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="https://ragchew.site/support">Support</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/timmorgan/ragchew.site">GitHub</a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-copy">
      Built by KI5ZDF &amp; KI5ZDG &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Data via NetLogger (not affiliated) &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Tim Morgan
    </p>
  </footer>

  <dialog id="beta-dialog">
    <h3>Become an Android Beta Tester</h3>
    <p>RagChew for Android isn't on the Play Store yet. If you'd like to help test it, send us your email address and we'll add you to the beta program.</p>
    <div class="dialog-actions">
      <a href="mailto:support@ragchew.app?subject=Android%20Beta%20Tester" class="btn btn-primary">Email Us to Sign Up</a>
      <button class="btn-close" onclick="document.getElementById('beta-dialog').close()">Cancel</button>
    </div>
  </dialog>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('beta-dialog').addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      if (e.target === this) this.close();
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>
